snippet.title: Furi Demake - The Chain - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Fight your way free in this 8-bit-inspired version of Furi's first boss fight against The Chain. Frantic action, nervous controls, a blend of shoot and sword fight reimagined in 90s style.

Furi Demake - The Chain out for free on Steam! https://bit.ly/FuriDemake-Steam

Links to all stores and platforms: https://linktr.ee/TheGameBakers
